This is a simple movie list reader program.
The program will read the input file named movies_sample_1.csv and prompt the user a menu of action they want to do as below: 
    1. Show movies released in the specified year
	2. Show highest rated movie for each year
	3. Show the title and year of release of all movies in a specific language
	4. Exit from the program

Use commend make to compile the program
Use the below commend to run the program 
    ./movies movies_sample_1.csv